title: Fix TitleExtractor adding extra | to unmatched titles
message:
Fix TitleExtractor adding extra | to unmatched titles

Java's String#split(String) takes a regex, not a simple string to
match, so "|" splits on "" or "" (splits every character), and then the
string gets concatenated back together with | between every character.
